- Just talking about love.

29:25.013 --> 29:29.894
And how, sometimes,
it only comes around once.

29:30.060 --> 29:31.500
And when it does,
you gotta grab it.

29:31.812 --> 29:33.610
- Yeah?
- You got to grab it and hold onto it

29:33.772 --> 29:36.776
because, uh, you never know.

29:36.942 --> 29:39.491
You never know. It can be gone.

29:41.196 --> 29:43.369
Just like that.

29:45.701 --> 29:47.453
[ALL GRuNTING]

