I haven't been beat up by idiot
businessmen since Wednesday.

30:05.512 --> 30:06.912
MAN: Come on,
let's get out of here.

30:16.565 --> 30:17.612
Thanks.

30:20.944 --> 30:22.617
There needs to be
a special on these.

30:22.779 --> 30:24.281
We've been selling
them like hotcakes.

30:24.448 --> 30:26.792
Never seen anything like it,
especially this time of year.

30:26.950 --> 30:28.543
Gazillions of mosquitoes.

30:28.702 --> 30:30.875
They feed on the decay.

30:31.038 --> 30:33.962
The mosquitoes feed on the decay.
That's why there's so many of them.

30:34.124 --> 30:36.004
