30:55.437 --> 30:58.065
I figured it out.
I know how to distribute the cure.

30:58.231 --> 30:59.278
Mosquitoes.

30:59.441 --> 31:00.988
- Mosquitoes?
- Mosquitoes, all right?

31:01.151 --> 31:04.121
We inject a certain population
of mosquitoes with the cure,

31:04.279 --> 31:05.997
we let them spread it
to the other animals.

31:06.156 --> 31:08.705
Mosquitoes feed on every type
of living species there is.

31:08.867 --> 31:11.120
I mean, birds, mammals,
reptiles, amphibians.

31:11.286 --> 31:13.414
Meaning when they bite,
they'll be passing it along.

31:13.580 --> 31:15.503
Not only that,
but they lay their eggs in water,

31:15.665 --> 31:18.043
so it'll be spread to all
sorts of water sources.

31:18.210 --> 31:21.339
Feeding holes, remote places we
could never even think of getting to.

31:21.505 --> 31:24.930
- This could work.
- It will work.

31:26.051 --> 31:27.598
Amelia, Jackson has...

31:27.761 --> 31:30.059
Athens just declared
a state of emergency.

31:30.430 --> 31:33.024
Seagulls took out a
dozen relay stations.

31:33.183 --> 31:35.436
Jackson found a way
to deliver the cure.

31:35.602 --> 31:37.122
We inject mosquitoes
and introduce them

31:37.270 --> 31:38.790
into the animal
population, all right?

31:38.939 --> 31:41.692
I've looked at this from every angle.
There is no possible downside.

31:41.858 --> 31:43.952
I'm afraid it doesn't matter.

31:44.111 --> 31:45.351
We just got a call from Zambia.

31:45.987 --> 31:47.067
The leopard they retrieved,

31:47.197 --> 31:50.371
apparently it migrated onto
land serviced by Reiden.

31:50.742 --> 31:53.040
So it's been contaminated.

31:53.203 --> 31:55.581
It's no longer
viable for the cure.

31:55.747 --> 31:58.796
