35:27.334 --> 35:29.132
I heard about that.

35:29.294 --> 35:33.299
There's also apparently secret
societies for cat lovers.

35:33.465 --> 35:35.183
Even before all this began,

35:35.342 --> 35:38.721
people who love cats should
have kept themselves hidden.

35:40.388 --> 35:41.560
Where you been, Abe?

35:45.143 --> 35:46.770
You know.

35:47.354 --> 35:50.107
Trying to sort things
out, I suppose.

35:50.857 --> 35:54.578
- And what'd you learn?
- Not much of anything, really.

35:55.195 --> 35:56.822
Except...

35:58.073 --> 36:03.204
These are not the days to retreat
from those you care about.

36:03.703 --> 36:08.004
In fact, these are the days
to do the very opposite.

36:09.793 --> 36:12.512
You know, no matter what
has happened up until now,

36:13.296 --> 36:15.390
we must continue.

36:16.007 --> 36:18.260
I mean,
things will get worse, yes.

36:18.426 --> 36:21.475
There will be failures, yes.
There will be suffering.

36:21.638 --> 36:23.606
But we must continue.

36:23.765 --> 36:25.483
The leopards are gone.

36:25.642 --> 36:29.738
So we find whatever is the next
leopard, the next solution.

36:29.896 --> 36:32.024
Jamie should not have
lost her life for nothing.

36:35.235 --> 36:36.782
