Posivak?

37:52.896 --> 37:53.943
Posivak.

38:00.028 --> 38:01.575
Oh, my God.

38:02.697 --> 38:04.199
Posivak.

38:08.870 --> 38:10.463
Posivak.

38:21.090 --> 38:24.139
