39:27.448 --> 39:29.416
MITCH: It really is you.

39:35.373 --> 39:37.876
It's really good
to hear your voice.

39:42.130 --> 39:44.599
MITCH: it's really
good to hear yours too.

39:51.890 --> 39:53.892
I still have it.

39:54.058 --> 39:56.186
I have the leopard.
I have the cure.

39:58.813 --> 40:00.406
Okay.

40:01.316 --> 40:02.363
You still have it.

40:09.741 --> 40:11.539
Hey, kids.

40:15.246 --> 40:17.465
- What happened to you?
- Cut myself snarking.

40:17.624 --> 40:19.752
