40:29.260 --> 40:30.637
Hey, here he is.

40:30.803 --> 40:32.851
Hey. Hello, professor.

40:33.389 --> 40:35.357
Hey, Chloe.

40:37.518 --> 40:38.565
CHLOE: Hi.

40:39.562 --> 40:42.441
All right, so, what's the plan?

40:42.607 --> 40:43.859
We drive to Delaware.

40:44.025 --> 40:46.574
There is a boat that
will take us to Jamie.

40:47.779 --> 40:49.781
- A boat?
- Yeah.

40:49.948 --> 40:53.122
It'll take 18 hours or so,
but, you know, air travel.

40:54.077 --> 40:57.377
Yeah, I'm okay not getting
on a plane for a while.

